Td(n)o(n):f link: iOS 10 Hidden Feature: Unlock your iPhone without a click
M(0)fz(14px) description: When Apple released iOS 10, the latest system software for the iPhone/iPad, it made a big deal out of the major features, like a redesigned Music app and contextual predictions in autocorrect.
